profile:
D&S renovations offers residential renovations services in Nova Scotia.  Full scope renovations, basements developments, kitchens, bathrooms renovations, exteriors and home additions are just some of the services offered by D&S.  With over 50 years of experience in the residential construction industry D&S Renovations has developed our services to meet the needs of all clients and their budgets. 

Please give us a call today to inquire about an estimate with one of our project developers.

profile:
Ultimate Bathroom Renovations is your one-stop solution for quality bath transformations.

We service Dartmouth, Halifax and the surrounding areas. We are proud supporting members of the BBB, the Nova Scotia Home Builders Association, Nova Scotia Construction Safety Association, and the Workers' Compensation Board Of Nova Scotia.
Our Halifax renovation services include bath remodelling, shower remodelling, tub to shower conversions and walk-in bathtub installations, with an array of quality acrylic and non-acrylic bath renovation products.
For full details visit www.ultimatebathroom.ca or call us today for your free in-home estimate on 902 292 2284 or email us at info@ultimatebathroom.ca
